values:
Tag. You're It.
(A) First, recommend to me:
1. a movie:
2. a book:
3. a musical artist, song, or album:

(B) I want everyone who reads this to ask me three questions, no more, no less. Ask me anything you want.

(C) Then I want you to go to your journal, copy and paste this allowing your friends to ask you anything.

:P Because you're the only one who does. XP Maraquan Meerca. :o SO PUFFY! ^_^ Mutant Meerca. Ya, ba-bae. o_0 No one gets it? NOOOOOOOO!!!! Maraquan Mynci. ^_^ So webby! Pirate Peophin. I just love that jacket. Msp Poogle. >.> I had the first one. I love it's defeated pose. Baby Pteri. :o Eggs pwn! Baby Quiggle. ^_^ Big-eyed! Quigukigirl Quiggle. I love the hair. :P Maraquan Scorchio. :D So cute. ^_^ And orange. And scaly. Maraquan Techo. I love his colours! Mutant Techo. :D It has all those cute spikes. Baby Tuskaninny. ^_^ More big eyes! Usukiboy Usul. I love the goatee. :P Baby Yurble. SO CUTE! Grey Yurble. I love how its ears droop. ^_^ Royalgirl Zafara. I love the dress. And that's all. Good day to you. :o I'm moving on October 21.

:P Here are my dream pets... yes, I'm BORED. Royalboy Acara. Big pimpin'. :P Alien Aishas. Just so cute, I want to lick it. But then that would stain the plastic helmet. Darigan Aisha. Looks so anorexic, I just wanna hug it. :3 Royalgirl Aisha. Love the dress and hat. Baby Bruce. Gotta love the big head. :P Maraquan Buzz. Claw-ness. :D Love all the Fruit Chias, but I love these the most. ^_^ Maraquan Chomby. I love the Loch Ness-ness. o_0 Baby Draik. More big-headedness. :D Faerie Draik. ^_^ SO CUTE! Maraquan Draik. Love the colours. Mutant Draik. :D SO COOL!!! ^_^ Tyrannian Draik. I love the thing on the head. :P Island Grundo. It has a 1337 mask! Grey Ixi. -licks it- It looks so cute! Coconut Jubjub. It's a coconut! :D So 1337. Maraquan Kau. Looks like Kau From the Sea. But is it beef or fish? Chokato Kiko. :o Love Chokatoness! Sponge Kiko. SO SPONGILICIOUS! Baby Kougra. Aw... looks so cute! ^_^ Maraquan Kougra. LOVE IT. Royalboy Kougra. I love the mane. Island Kyrii. I love the outfit. My Lenny Real-Life Bird Set. I love them. :D And that's all for part I. Part II will come tomorrow. ^_^

I was bored, so I decided to do this list of avatars I would have if mrkmrk36 was not frozen. (One of them ;)) Lemme count them. :P That's 140. Out of 169. And that's not counting if I got any random avatars (Jester) or if I got extremely lucky and get Petpetsitter, etc. :o PNG! I would be at Vicki's level!!! :o -freaks out-

OMG!  I beat NQ2!
I'm playing on Evil mode.
And it's EVIL! :K
